FT  04 SEP 92 / The Lex Column: Ladbroke
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Ladbroke's shares have taken a beating since the election. Yielding around
10 per cent - some 50 per cent above the sector average - investors may ask
if the selling has gone too far. Judging by yesterday's interim results, it
is too soon for a re-evaluation. Hotels and property remain dependent on the
