 ------------------------------------------------------------------
                      Retail   Office   Industrial   All Properties
 ------------------------------------------------------------------
Year to July 92        -1.6    -13.4      -5.6          -7.0
Quarter to July 92     -0.6     -3.6      -2.5          -2.1
