<HEADLINE>
FT  03 SEP 92 / UK Company News: Morgan Crucible Pounds 10m purchases
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Morgan Crucible has completed five acquisitions costing a total Pounds
10.3m. The companies are expected to achieve a combined annual operating
profit of more than Pounds 2.5m.
The companies acquired are the Lodge ceramics division of Smiths Industries,
a majority interest in Refractories and Mineral Investments BV, the clean
room wipes business and related assets of Coventry Manufacturing of Los
Angeles, Epirez of Australia, a manufacturer of speciality chemicals, and
the cutting fluid business and related assets of Tapmatic Corporation of
California.
</TEXT>
