FT  03 SEP 92 / UK Company News: Beckenham reduces debt further
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Beckenham Group, USM-quoted engineer, said that its arbitration proceedings
against British Telecommunications had been settled as to the sum of Pounds
2.25m.
Together with the proceeds of the recent Pounds 1.9m rights issue, bank
borrowings are reduced to about Pounds 3m.
