tonne unit (10 kg) WO, cif, 53-62 (same).
VANADIUM: European free market, min. 98 per cent, Dollars a lb VO, cif,
2.00-2.15 (same).
URANIUM: Nuexco exchange value, Dollars per lb, UO, 7.75 (same).
